        content="AI Chat Application by MBK Tech Studio - A simple web interface for chatting with AI models including Gemini 2.0, Gemini 1.5 variants, and NVIDIA Llama Nemotron models. Open-source and customizable.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="AI Chat, ChatAPI, MBK Tech Studio, Gemini AI, NVIDIA, Llama Nemotron, AI Assistant, Chatbot, Open Source, Node.js">
